<MethodEndpoint
  method={"delete"}
  path={"/spaces/{space_id}/properties/{property_id}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



This endpoint “deletes” a property by marking it as archived. The deletion process is performed safely and is subject to rate limiting. It returns the property’s details after it has been archived. Proper error handling is in place for situations such as when the property isn’t found or the deletion cannot be performed because of permission issues.
